; ABB Robotic Script (IRB 1200)
; Chain Assembly Module
CONST num nLinks := 203;
CONST num wireDiam := 0.85;
VAR robtarget pHome := [[150,0,300],[1,0,0,0],[0,0,0,0]];

PROC main()
  InitSystem;
  FOR i FROM 1 TO nLinks DO
    WireFeeder_Feed(wireDiam);
    FormingDie_Actuate;
    IF i > 1 THEN
      VisionLocatePrevLink;
      Interlock_Cycle;
    ENDIF
    SolderHead_Active;
    LaserSolder_Fire(8ms, 12J);
  ENDFOR
  AttachClasp;
  PolishSequence_MultiStage;
  Final_QC_Check;
ENDPROC

Manufacturing Safety Protocols & Compliance

Laser Safety

Requires appropriate laser safety glasses (OD specified for wavelength), interlocked enclosures, and regular calibration/power checks for soldering and engraving systems.

Material Handling

Delicate handling by robotic grippers is essential for the soft 22K gold to prevent deformation or scratches. Gripper pressure must be precisely calibrated.

Dust Recovery

High-efficiency dust extraction and recovery systems (HEPA) are mandatory for valuable and potentially hazardous gold dust generated during polishing.
